•
This weekend the Shop employees challenged the Innetech crew to a special Game of Skate tournament in the Pro Course.
—
The rules were simple; 
• 2 skaters from each crew 
• 3 games of skate 
 - One game on Flat
 - Two games on Pro Course obstacles 
—
With bragging rights (and lunch) on the line the two squads battled it out for SPoT supremacy...who did you have ur money on??!
—
Teams
Innetech: @rolo.c & @marsefarmer_ 
Shop Guys: @timgasiorski & @skatestoppers_ 
—
📱: @bowser_media_lab 
#SPoTSkateBattle #SPoTTeam #SPoTTampa

#spottampa #wheelbite #girlskateboards #volcolm

The new @vansskate Wayvee was built from the ground up with input from
Tyson Peterson and other Vans skate team riders, available only at finer skate shops. 🔴🟡🟢

The @tysonpeterson_ Wayvee feature a suede and translucent mesh upper for durability and breathability. The WAFFLECUP outsole is the best of both worlds, providing superior board feel, maximum support, and durability. 🔴🟡🟢

🛹 @sambellipanni /// 📹📸 @shailfish

node.text:
Always consistent, the @louielopez Pro Mid, like the low top, is designed specifically for skateboarding by the @converse_cons team rider himself. A premium, suede upper with butted seams and rubber backing helps reduce friction and provide durability. The CX foam sockliner adds cushioning and impact protection, and a traction rubber outsole allows for better grip. It's all Louie's vision, every element to skate at his best. 

Available now in store and online in black/white & white/black ⚫️⚪️

#conversecons #louielopez #SPoTTampa
